-- Migration 007: Populate num_auxiliaries in cbhpm_codes from CBHPM 2022.
--
-- Source: CBHPM-2022_versao-agosto-2023.pdf, Chapter 3 (N° de Aux. column).
-- Codes from Chapters 1 (Consultas), 2 (Clínica), and 4 (Diagnóstico) have
-- no auxiliary column in the CBHPM 2022 table; they remain 0.
--
-- Idempotent: UPDATE … WHERE num_auxiliaries IS DISTINCT FROM excluded value
-- so repeated runs touch only rows that actually differ.

